{"metadata":{"externalID":"s:ScS12ContinuationV13onTerminationyAB0C0Oyx__GYbcSgvp","role":"symbol","title":"onTermination","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onTermination"},{"kind":"text","text":": ("},{"kind":"attribute","text":"@Sendable"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScS12ContinuationV11TerminationO","text":"Termination"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void"},{"kind":"text","text":")?"}],"modules":[{"name":"Swift","relatedModules":[]}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A callback to invoke when canceling iteration of an asynchronous"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"stream."}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/AsyncStream/Continuation/Termination"],"title":"Handling Termination","generated":true,"anchor":"Handling-Termination"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["/documentation/swift/asyncstream/continuation/ontermination"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onTermination"},{"kind":"text","text":": ("},{"kind":"attribute","text":"@Sendable"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/AsyncStream/Continuation/Termination","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScS12ContinuationV11TerminationO","text":"Termination"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void"},{"kind":"text","text":")? { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonmutating"},{"kind":"te